BinaryTree

Class SearchTreeProcedures

  • java.lang.Object
    • BinaryTree.SearchTreeProcedures

  • public class SearchTreeProcedures
extends java.lang.Object
    Last edited 1/5/2021
    A collection of static procedures commonly used on binary search trees.
    The syntax before each method is to allow for generic typing. This allows the methods to run on nodes that use any kind of comparable object.
